00:31:54.400 --> 00:32:00.360 align:middle line:84%
And then from behind us a row
of 30 insects came up behind us.

00:32:00.360 --> 00:32:02.690 align:middle line:84%
And they came along
the side of me.

00:32:02.690 --> 00:32:05.310 align:middle line:84%
There were smaller ones,
kind of like a beetle,

00:32:05.310 --> 00:32:07.650 align:middle line:84%
