00:32:10.740 --> 00:32:12.720 align:middle line:90%
They hopped, and they had wings.

00:32:12.720 --> 00:32:14.190 align:middle line:90%
And I got a shot off.

00:32:14.190 --> 00:32:15.200 align:middle line:90%
I was in the middle.

00:32:15.200 --> 00:32:16.000 align:middle line:90%
I was mid air.

00:32:16.000 --> 00:32:17.790 align:middle line:84%
I was jumping from
a dune to a dune,

00:32:17.790 --> 00:32:21.420 align:middle line:90%
and I finally shot the gun.

00:32:21.420 --> 00:32:24.550 align:middle line:84%
And of course I
didn't hit anything.

00:32:24.550 --> 00:32:28.650 align:middle line:84%
And one came up behind me
and took my arm right off--

00:32:28.650 --> 00:32:29.920 align:middle line:90%
the gun and the arm--

00:32:29.920 --> 00:32:30.960 align:middle line:90%
bit it right off.

00:32:30.960 --> 00:32:33.970 align:middle line:90%
And I fell, and it stood on me.

00:32:33.970 --> 00:32:37.420 align:middle line:84%
And I was in complete shock,
and I thought, I'm dead.

00:32:37.420 --> 00:32:42.400 align:middle line:84%
I heard the other two guys
in front of me get killed.

00:32:42.400 --> 00:32:45.730 align:middle line:84%
They were eaten or
bit up into pieces.

00:32:45.730 --> 00:32:48.170 align:middle line:90%
I later had found their body.

00:32:48.170 --> 00:32:50.330 align:middle line:90%
I sat there.

00:32:50.330 --> 00:32:51.320 align:middle line:90%
It held me down.

00:32:51.320 --> 00:32:53.000 align:middle line:90%
It stood on me.

00:32:53.000 --> 00:32:55.460 align:middle line:84%
And I remember just
saying over and over,

00:32:55.460 --> 00:32:57.380 align:middle line:84%
please don't kill me,
please don't kill me.

00:32:57.380 --> 00:33:00.300 align:middle line:84%
All of that psychological
training went out the window.

00:33:00.300 --> 00:33:02.240 align:middle line:84%
Everything that they
had programmed me was--

00:33:02.240 --> 00:33:03.740 align:middle line:90%
I didn't want to die.

00:33:03.740 --> 00:33:05.780 align:middle line:90%
I didn't want to die.

00:33:05.780 --> 00:33:08.450 align:middle line:84%
I knew that I had
somewhere else in life.

00:33:08.450 --> 00:33:11.600 align:middle line:84%
Somehow-- I don't know how it
did it-- but it picked me up,

00:33:11.600 --> 00:33:14.990 align:middle line:84%
and a third kind
of bug came over

00:33:14.990 --> 00:33:17.210 align:middle line:84%
from where the other
two-- came over the dune.

00:33:17.210 --> 00:33:19.210 align:middle line:84%
And it was much different,
