00:33:19.210 --> 00:33:21.090 align:middle line:84%
It moved strange, and
it moved its head.

00:33:21.090 --> 00:33:26.180 align:middle line:84%
It had antenna, and they had
balls on top of each other.

00:33:26.180 --> 00:33:26.980 align:middle line:90%
It had antenna.

00:33:26.980 --> 00:33:29.260 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: And you're bleeding
pretty badly, I would imagine.

00:33:29.260 --> 00:33:30.590 align:middle line:84%
>>RODRIGUES: I was
in shock from--

00:33:30.590 --> 00:33:31.430 align:middle line:90%
I had no arm.

00:33:31.430 --> 00:33:33.138 align:middle line:84%
It walked up to me
slowly, and it kind of

00:33:33.138 --> 00:33:34.817 align:middle line:90%
moved its head awkwardly.

00:33:34.817 --> 00:33:37.400 align:middle line:84%
And when it got close enough to
me where it was face to face--

00:33:37.400 --> 00:33:39.990 align:middle line:90%
and I was just totally in shock.

00:33:39.990 --> 00:33:41.700 align:middle line:84%
I couldn't believe
what was going on.

00:33:41.700 --> 00:33:45.600 align:middle line:90%
I was totally beside myself.

00:33:45.600 --> 00:33:48.140 align:middle line:84%
When they say about people in
car accidents and the things

00:33:48.140 --> 00:33:49.550 align:middle line:90%
they can go into shock--

00:33:49.550 --> 00:33:51.130 align:middle line:90%
I was in that.

00:33:51.130 --> 00:33:53.420 align:middle line:84%
And I just kept begging,
please don't kill me, please

00:33:53.420 --> 00:33:54.440 align:middle line:90%
don't kill me.

00:33:54.440 --> 00:33:55.677 align:middle line:90%
Please, I don't want to die.

00:33:55.677 --> 00:33:56.510 align:middle line:90%
I don't want to die.

00:33:56.510 --> 00:33:57.385 align:middle line:90%
Please don't kill me.

00:33:57.385 --> 00:34:00.600 align:middle line:90%
I was just in tears.

00:34:00.600 --> 00:34:04.400 align:middle line:84%
And when he got up close to
me face to face with me--

00:34:04.400 --> 00:34:06.060 align:middle line:90%
