like standing-- literally

00:34:27.290 --> 00:34:29.340 align:middle line:90%
just like standing in the room.

00:34:29.340 --> 00:34:31.699 align:middle line:84%
>>JAY: Oh, so he's going
through your memories?

00:34:31.699 --> 00:34:34.200 align:middle line:84%
>>RODRIGUES: Yes, and he went
through my entire time up

00:34:34.200 --> 00:34:35.000 align:middle line:90%
until--

00:34:35.000 --> 00:34:37.909 align:middle line:84%
he went inside the
base where I was,

00:34:37.909 --> 00:34:42.000 align:middle line:84%
and he showed me the cubicle
where I was sleeping.

00:34:42.000 --> 00:34:42.830 align:middle line:90%
It was empty.

00:34:42.830 --> 00:34:47.690 align:middle line:84%
Nobody else there but me
and him standing there.

00:34:47.690 --> 00:34:51.020 align:middle line:84%
It was like a dream, but it was
a waking memory that he was--

00:34:51.020 --> 00:34:54.875 align:middle line:84%
and the whole time he
was explaining it I

00:34:54.875 --> 00:34:56.250 align:middle line:84%
couldn't hear what
he was saying,

00:34:56.250 --> 00:34:58.670 align:middle line:84%
but I could perceive
that he was describing

00:34:58.670 --> 00:35:01.680 align:middle line:84%
the scene to something
else, to somebody else.

00:35:01.680 --> 00:35:05.300 align:middle line:84%
Not the other insects around
us, but something far away.

00:35:05.300 --> 00:35:07.310 align:middle line:90%
He was describing what he saw.

00:35:07.310 --> 00:35:09.362 align:middle line:84%
And it went through
the entire time,

00:35:09.362 --> 00:35:10.820 align:middle line:84%
