up-- it showed me

00:35:10.820 --> 00:35:13.130 align:middle line:84%
my living room of
my childhood house

00:35:13.130 --> 00:35:15.750 align:middle line:84%
that I was taken from that
I didn't have memories of.

00:35:15.750 --> 00:35:18.120 align:middle line:84%
And he said, this
is who you are.

00:35:18.120 --> 00:35:19.310 align:middle line:90%
This is who you are.

00:35:19.310 --> 00:35:20.150 align:middle line:84%
That was the other
