00:35:20.150 --> 00:35:21.860 align:middle line:84%
We're going to find
out your purpose.

00:35:21.860 --> 00:35:26.060 align:middle line:84%
We're going to find your
purpose, what your purpose is.

00:35:26.060 --> 00:35:27.560 align:middle line:84%
And at the end, he
said your purpose

00:35:27.560 --> 00:35:30.420 align:middle line:90%
