00:35:30.420 --> 00:35:32.510 align:middle line:84%
You don't have a
purpose for killing.

00:35:32.510 --> 00:35:34.750 align:middle line:90%
You can live.

00:35:34.750 --> 00:35:37.550 align:middle line:84%
And I went out, and I
woke up the next morning

00:35:37.550 --> 00:35:38.750 align:middle line:90%
